.TH man 8 "25 Aug 2018" "1.0" "Addalias man page"
.SH NAME
addalias \- create a new alias for your command 
.SH SYNOPSIS
addalias
.SH DESCRIPTION
addalias is high level shell program to add aliases to your terminal. It prompts users to type in the name of the new alias and the command to be used.
.SH OPTIONS
The addalias does not take any options.
.SH BUGS
No known bugs. If any found, please create an issue on github (https://github.com/newtonkiragu/aliases/issues)
.SH AUTHOR
Newton Karanu (karanunewton4@gmail.com)